00:00:38.350 --> 00:00:42.370
the moment, I'm actually giving my hair a
bit of a break from colour and this shampoo

00:00:42.370 --> 00:00:46.290
and conditioner is really going to put that
moisture back in my hair, it helps with my

00:00:46.290 --> 00:00:51.540
dry ends and it smells of mint, it smells
so, so beautiful and leaves my hair just so

00:00:51.540 --> 00:00:56.330
soft. Next up I'm going to use my Head &amp; Shoulders
thick &amp; strong extra thickening treatment.

