00:01:17.620 --> 00:01:22.750
gives me so much volume when I blow dry it
which is exactly what I want for this look.

00:01:22.750 --> 00:01:27.250
Then I'm going to use my Aussie Aussome Volume
Miracle Recharge lightweight conditioning

00:01:27.250 --> 00:01:32.120
spray. I do not even need to go on enough
about how much I love Aussie products. I'm

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:36.730
a massive fan of their 3 minute miracle conditioner.
This one is really good if you, again like

00:01:36.730 --> 00:01:41.000
me, have dry ends because this is really good
from mid length downward to the ends just

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:44.659
to give you a little bit of conditioning.
You can put it in wet or dry hair and literally

00:01:44.659 --> 00:01:48.500
just comb it through and blow dry it out and
